    "lyrics": {
      "text": "The sol-diers stand--ing___ guard_____ at Thy__ tomb,__ O__ my Sav---iour, be-came as__ dead__ on___ see-----ing the__ light--ning--like An---gel who preached to___ the wom---en___ of____ Thine a-ris--ing,___ O Ho-----ly Lord. Thee___ we glo---ri---fy,___ Who hast a--bol--ished__ cor-rup---tion; Thee___ do we___ a---dore,___ Who from the__ grave__ hast__ a-ris---en and Who a--lone art__ our____ God.__"
    }
